{"tid":2331464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱達昌發港難財 直擊英國曼城2萬伙「香港城」","createTime":"2020-12-18T20:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T23:46:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a77f73d848a005b0fa6ef238f88cdba4bcce7c92","tid":2331464,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T20:55:42.000Z","msg":"香港掀起移英潮，本港三大地產商新世界（017）﹑新地（016）及長實（1135）早已涉足英國房地產市場，但發展項目的體積﹑規劃及步伐卻遠遠不及遠東發展（035，下稱遠展），尤其是遠展與曼城市議會合作發展的「巨無霸」項目Northern Gateway有約2萬伙，海量供應「食正」今次港人移英潮。然而，本土研究社成員陳劍青直斥遠展的邱達昌一邊撐《港區國安法》，摧毀有線新聞部，另一邊廂卻大舉投資英國樓，受惠被壓迫而引發的移民潮，完全是「吃人血饅頭！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201218/JGZ7XVLNIRCOVBT7S2TPZVLCHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201218%2FJGZ7XVLNIRCOVBT7S2TPZVLCHY%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=0be39231\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201218%2FJGZ7XVLNIRCOVBT7S2TPZVLCHY%2F&h=fa099904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201218/JGZ7XVLNIRCOVBT7S2TPZVLCHY/</a>"},{"pid":"086b704f1716548837f667d99c3feeec762c79e6","tid":2331464,"uid":28181,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T21:16:58.000Z","msg":"撐《港區國安法》-&gt;英國立左馬格尼茨基人權問之彼可立即凍結佢英國資產~"},{"pid":"dae9cde2029818ca66bef6df40f46dc833863bc9","tid":2331464,"uid":196329,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"086b704f1716548837f667d99c3feeec762c79e6","tid":2331464,"uid":28181,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T21:16:58.000Z","msg":"撐《港區國安法》-&gt;英國立左馬格尼茨基人權問之彼可立即凍結佢英國資產~"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T21:19:40.000Z","msg":"打少陣飛機啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d340271c